{"id": "13886", "post": "<div class=\"post-13886 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers\" id=\"post-13886\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/dont-miss-the-black-friday-deals/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Don\u2019t miss the Black Friday Deals!</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> November 6, 2017 @ 3:27 pm, by Matt Zelasko</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"https://www.lowendbox.com\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/its-coming.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/its-coming.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"300\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hello LowEndBox! I wanted to let everyone know about what\u2019s going to be happening here this year for Black Friday and Cyber Monday!</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We\u2019ve been working with quite a few providers in order to get the best possible deals offered this year, and throughout the process we decided that we\u2019re going to do something a little different. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On Black Friday itself, we\u2019re going to be doing one \u201cMega Post\u201d with 10 offers from 10 different providers. There will be a great mix of offers: Great yearly pricing, great monthly pricing, OpenVZ, KVM, Storage VPS, Bare metal dedicated, etc\u2026 so we\u2019re definitely going to have a little something for everyone.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What we have essentially done is get these providers to compete to make it into the Top 10 \u2013 and the results have been phenomenal. Most of these providers are truly putting their best foot forward and submitting some of the most incredible offers we\u2019ve ever seen. That obviously benefits you \u2013 the readers.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition to the Top 10, we\u2019re going to have a few exclusive offers posted during Black Friday, Cyber Monday, and the days in between \u2013 so keep an eye out for those as well!</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lastly, there\u2019s also going to be a few offers that we\u2019re exclusively doing via email and social media, so make sure you sign up for our Newsletter (one lucky email subscriber gets a $50 Amazon Gift Card!) below and keep an eye out on&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/lowendnetwork\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Twitter</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lowendofficial\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Facebook</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">!</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fill out the form below \u2013 1 lucky person is going to be selected to win a $50 Amazon Gift Card! Good luck and we\u2019re sure you\u2019re going to love all the Black Friday offers! See you then!&nbsp;</span></p><p>[captainform id=\u201d975711\u2033]</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fdont-miss-the-black-friday-deals%2F&amp;t=Don%27t%20miss%20the%20Black%20Friday%20Deals%21\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on